  "detailed_description": "<strong>“每个城市的角落里，都孕育着一片罪恶的土壤。”</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397070/extras/f9a8fe29ced0c7631851f2cec4f5a33e.poster.avif?t=1772621940\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397070/extras/f9a8fe29ced0c7631851f2cec4f5a33e.webm?t=1772621940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397070/extras/f9a8fe29ced0c7631851f2cec4f5a33e.mp4?t=1772621940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你在游戏中扮演的主人公是一位法医系的大学生。在收到损友发来的“福利视频”后，一位白衣女子伴随着接连不断的噩梦闯入了你平静的生活中。在接受神秘人的游戏邀请之后，你被迫卷入了一系列连环杀人案之中。随着对案情的深入调查，你向警方、同学已经前辈们展现了超常的尸检才能和推理能力，令众人刮目相看。并逐渐发现这一系列凶案都指向了七年前的福利院案件。你在现实和过去的交织中终于让福利院的幕后交易浮出水面，而自己生父的死因和弟弟的去向也慢慢清晰。在不知不觉中，你已经深入到了邪恶的最深处。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >※收集线索，推理案情，出示证据，审讯嫌疑人</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397070/extras/1fb470696c49d0c183c48a2417c1012e.poster.avif?t=1772621940\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397070/extras/1fb470696c49d0c183c48a2417c1012e.webm?t=1772621940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397070/extras/1fb470696c49d0c183c48a2417c1012e.mp4?t=1772621940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >※与游戏内角色开启聊天，了解隐藏在TA们背后的故事。伴随真人语音、表情等要素，呈现真人聊天的感觉</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397070/extras/4c1ca9ebeb51b54e070ad77949782057.poster.avif?t=1772621940\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397070/extras/4c1ca9ebeb51b54e070ad77949782057.webm?t=1772621940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397070/extras/4c1ca9ebeb51b54e070ad77949782057.mp4?t=1772621940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >※深入、多元化的破案体验，满足你对侦探游戏的全部期待</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397070/extras/9739b5444ca7f0186b7e21f5d0b183e3.poster.avif?t=1772621940\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397070/extras/9739b5444ca7f0186b7e21f5d0b183e3.webm?t=1772621940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397070/extras/9739b5444ca7f0186b7e21f5d0b183e3.mp4?t=1772621940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >※超过50个结局、超过50段分格漫画式过场动画与40万字剧本</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397070/extras/249d6af5eb708f1a5563dc6daf9b1f63.poster.avif?t=1772621940\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397070/extras/249d6af5eb708f1a5563dc6daf9b1f63.webm?t=1772621940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397070/extras/249d6af5eb708f1a5563dc6daf9b1f63.mp4?t=1772621940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
